E. A. FULGHUM and R. E. Bricken, Appellants, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 6599. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. March 20, 1933. Rehearing Denied April 21, 1983. Ion L. Farris and M. H. Myerson, both of Jacksonville, Fla., for appellants. W. P. Hughes, U. S. Atty., of Jacksonville, Fla.

Before BRYAN, FOSTER, and SIBLEY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment is affirmed.
